ActHeritage Railway Stations Protection Act
SubjectVia Rail Canada - Alterations at 36 of its railway stations
PrecisOrder authorizing VIA RAIL CANADA to complete a limited range of alterations at 36 of its railway stations in order to protect and preserve the heritage character of these stations.
